English:
../BIOCOM
shortwave transmission intercepted@27mhz
meta3.date_stamp(570429.162633)

//transcript follows...

UNIDENTIFIED MALE
This is Francisco Del Pireo, Interim Director WHO Europe, broadcasting from our Milan [inaudible] on behalf of Dr. Rutermayer. On the 28th April, 2057, the Milan office received a [inaudible] transmission from the head of the Daylight Mission team. They have [inaudible] city of Progreso in the Yucatan Peninsula, near the mining facility known as Garganta. The team encountered no resistance during their journey, and report that all team members are healthy and continuing the search for a vaccine to the NAM virus.

../BIOCOM.
.. transcript ends//
intercept log updated
alert system flagged
